# game/Kyou 14.rpy:120
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_621984e9:

    # s casual "I know what you are thinking. And yes, this impulse of mine is... somewhat confusing me, to tell you the truth." with dissolve
    s casual "Sé lo que estás pensando. Y sí, este impulso que tengo me es... algo confuso, para ser sincera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:121
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d07cdeea:

    # s alert_sleep "I had thought, once you removed my compulsion to process hypnosis automatically as \"wonderful\", that I would come to resent what you did with me." with dissolve
    s alert_sleep "Había pensado que, una vez removieras la imposición de procesar la hipnosis automáticamente como \"maravillosa\", resentiría lo que hiciste conmigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:122
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3bea040d:

    # s "That my feelings would differ drastically from the girl I saw in that video, looking so... contented, to drop into trance for you."
    s "Que mis sentimientos diferirían drásticamente de los de la chica que vi en ese video, que lucía tan... dichosa de caer en trance ante ti."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:123
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_01f0b097:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "But there is no post-hypnotic conditioning to explain away my compulsions this time. I should be able to trust my feelings on the matter." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Pero no hay acondicionamiento posthipnótico que explique mis impulsos esta vez. Debería poder confiar en mis sentimientos al respecto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:124
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0ac1e292:

    # s "And my feelings are..."
    s "Y mis sentimientos son..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:127
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ef479b8f:

    # "Sayori pauses to draw an uncomfortable-looking breath."
    "Sayori hace una pausa y respira con incomodidad."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:129
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_075ddae9:

    # s alert_concerned_right blush "I will just admit it... Hypnosis continues to interest me." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right blush "Lo admitiré de una vez… La hipnosis aún me interesa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:130
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0b4072c3:

    # s alert_sleeptalk_concerned "To be hypnotized... interests me." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk_concerned "Ser hipnotizada... me interesa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:132
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5c5624d9:

    # s casual_folded alert_concerned "I still remember the sense of liberation I felt, when I could sleep comfortably without a single concern to weigh upon my mind." with dissolve
    s casual_folded alert_concerned "Todavía recuerdo la sensación de liberación que sentí cuando pude dormir con comodidad sin una sola preocupación haciendo eco en mi mente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:133
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_572ffdd7:

    # s "No anxieties. No stresses. No pain of any kind..."
    s "Sin ansiedades. Sin estrés. Sin dolor de ningún tipo..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:134
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fee9fa51:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "And while I could not possibly afford to live in such a carefree manner, I cannot return to how I was. This past week has shown me that..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Y si bien no podría permitirme vivir en un estado tan despreocupado, no puedo regresar a lo que fui. Esta última semana me lo ha mostrado..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:135
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f7cbb81b:

    # s alert_smile_right "So I would like to indulge. From time to time." with dissolve
    s alert_smile_right "Por lo que me gustaría darme gusto. De vez en cuando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:136
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4bc64da4:

    # "So... this isn't just an experiment we're doing here."
    "O sea que... esto no es solo un experimento."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:137
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_842b8a93:

    # "She's expecting to enjoy it. And she's trusting me with this knowledge completely."
    "Piensa disfrutarlo. Y confía completamente en mí y en mi conocimiento."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:138
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_15dbfabb:

    # "That's... wow, that's a lot for me to get excited about, let alone what's running through her head right now."
    "Eso... guau, eso me da muchas razones para emocionarme, sin mencionar lo que está pasando por su cabeza."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:148
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4051a3f1:

    # "Sayori then gets up and plants herself down on her bed, arranging herself much like she did the last time I was here."
    "Entonces Sayori se levanta y se sienta en su cama, acomodándose más o menos como la última vez que estuve aquí."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:149
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3bd9fc74:

    # s alert_neutral_right "So, I am anxious to get started, Kyou." with dissolve
    s alert_neutral_right "Bueno, ansío comenzar, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:150
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f929aae9:

    # "I'm about to ask about specifics. Like, did she have anything in mind besides just a \"doll\"?"
    "Tal vez deba pedir especificaciones. O sea, ¿tiene algo en mente además de una simple \"muñeca\"?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:151
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0502d0f6:

    # "Does she seriously want me to go nuts on the idea? There's got to be some sort of catch."
    "¿En serio quiere que me vuelva loco con la idea? Debe haber alguna clase de truco."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:152
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_500a57a3:

    # "... Or does she not think I can do it without the penlight? Is that what she's trying to prove?"
    "... ¿O será que no cree que pueda hacerlo sin la linterna? ¿Es eso lo que intenta probar?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:153
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b189c219:

    # s "Kyou, the consternation is written plainly on your face and let me tell you, you're worrying too much." with dissolve
    s "Kyou, la consternación está escrita claramente en tu rostro y déjame decirte que te preocupas demasiado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:154
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f308414f:

    # "But then, when I think back..."
    "Pero, cuando pienso en el pasado..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:155
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9668cc09:

    # s "Just do the task that is set as you see fit." with dissolve
    s "Solo haz el trabajo que consideres más apto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:157
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5a1e72c5:

    # "Sayori's had faith in me since we started." with dissolve
    "Sayori tuvo fe en mí desde que empezamos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:158
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_de85dded:

    # s "And then we can both leave our worries behind."
    s "Y ambos podremos dejar nuestras preocupaciones atrás."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:159
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a5c192d8:

    # "She wouldn't set me up to fail."
    "Ella no me guiaría al fracaso."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:160
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_33daa7f1:

    # s alert_happy "Let us enjoy this." with dissolve
    s alert_happy "Hay que disfrutarlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:161
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4295874b:

    # ks casual smile "Yeah. Yeah, you're right."
    ks casual smile "Sí. Sí, tienes razón."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:162
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e8a2d1c1:

    # "Okay, so I gotta think this through. Like a proper hypnotist."
    "De acuerdo, tengo que pensarlo bien. Como un buen hipnotista."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:163
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2ba790fc:

    # s casual alert_smile_right noblush "Good. Now I assume I need to take a relaxed position, but besides that I am relying on your direction, Kyou." with dissolve
    s casual alert_smile_right noblush "Bien. Pues asumo que debo adoptar una posición relajada, pero más allá de eso, espero tu dirección, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:164
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cc83e020:

    # "Sayori's whole deal is learning and study. Even though I can trust her to relax and focus for me, she might still end up over-analysing what's happening."
    "A Sayori le encanta el estudio y el aprendizaje. Si bien puedo confiar en que se relaje y se concentre en mí, aun así puede que termine analizando demasiado lo que está pasando. "

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:165
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3a9d531b:

    # "And that's going to complicate things when I'm trying to induce her into a trance."
    "Y eso complicará las cosas cuando intente inducirla al trance."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:166
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e65b4872:

    # "I should do something about that. Attack her critical thinking until it's forced to shut down."
    "Debo encargarme de eso. Atacar su pensamiento crítico hasta que se vea obligado a apagarse."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:169
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_dfdcda35:

    # "And somewhere, in the pile of written hypnosis scripts I have on my phone, I might have just the thing."
    "Y por aquí, entre esta pila de guiones de hipnosis que tengo en mi teléfono, tengo justo lo que necesito."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:175
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d76e58e5:

    # k "Okay Sayori, here's what we're gonna do."
    k "Muy bien Sayori, esto es lo que vamos a hacer."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:171
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8244c842:

    # "Yeah, this one. I wrote it myself. I think this will work well on her."
    "Sí, este. Yo mismo lo escribí. Creo que funcionará bien con ella."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:178
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bb771ee7:

    # k "You're sitting there nice and relaxed, and that's good, but I also want you to close your eyes."
    k "Estás ahí sentada, muy relajada, y eso es bueno, pero también quiero que cierres los ojos."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:176
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8a75330b:

    # "Sayori nods gently as she lets her eyes close." with dissolve
    "Sayori asiente con gentileza y deja que sus ojos se cierren." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:181
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_067af6c5:

    # k "Good. So I'm thinking there's a fun way to do this. We're going to play a simple game."
    k "Bien. Me parece que hay una forma divertida de hacer esto. Jugaremos un juego sencillo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:178
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d4591006:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Is that so?" with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Ya veo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:180
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_124fb2d6:

    # "Nodding to myself, I talk to her while glancing at the notes I have here on the screen." with dissolve
    "Asintiendo para mí mismo, le hablo mientras miro las notas que tengo aquí en la pantalla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:186
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_93994cda:

    # k "Yeah. So currently your eyes are closed. Not open or unclosed. But soon, I'm going to start counting."
    k "Sí. Pues bien, en este momento tus ojos están cerrados. Ni abiertos ni no cerrados."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:187
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7b85deb2:

    # k "I'll count up. Or down. Or maybe up, then down, but what's important is that your eyes are closed for every odd, not even, number that I count on."
    k "Voy a contar. Al derecho. O al revés. O tal vez al derecho, luego al revés. Pero lo que importa es que tus ojos estén cerrados con cada número non, no par, que cuente."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:188
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_983900fe:

    # k "And that means when I count a number that's not odd. A number that's even, not odd at all, I need your eyes to open. Understood?"
    k "Lo que significa que, cuando cuente un número no non. Un número que sea par y nada non, necesito que tus ojos se abran. ¿Entendido?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:184
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bbb2e167:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "That is a rather convoluted way of saying I need to open my eyes for even numbers and close them for odd..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Esa es una manera muy enrevesada de decir que debo abrir los ojos en los números pares y cerrarlos en los nones..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:185
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_881b21f3:

    # s "But yes, Kyou, I understand the game we're playing."
    s "Pero sí, Kyou, entiendo lo que estamos jugando."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:187
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_13d6a7f4:

    # "I mean, yeah. And it's good she understands this part at the very least, else the whole thing falls apart." with dissolve
    "Bueno, sí. Y es bueno que por lo menos entienda esta parte, de lo contrario, todo se viene abajo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:189
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1d800ede:

    # "And she's obviously aware there's a method to this madness. She'll play along and focus on every single word I say to her."
    "Y obviamente está consciente de que hay un método detrás de esta locura. Me seguirá la corriente y se concentrará en cada palabra que le diga."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:190
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_92aa3096:

    # "So let's see how well her critical mind holds up after a few more minutes of this nonsense."
    "Así que veamos si su sentido crítico puede seguir el ritmo luego de algunos minutos de estos disparates."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:197
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6b8e2275:

    # k "Very good. So I'm going to start the count at... one!"
    k "Qué bien. Así que empezaré a contar desde el... ¡uno!"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:192
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e1554201:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:193
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_da7de0be:

    # "I pause for effect, but nothing happens as Sayori remains unmoved."
    "Pauso por efecto, pero nada ocurre. Sayori no mueve ni un músculo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:194
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_45497f25:

    # "Not that I was expecting anything different. She'd be very embarrassed if I caught her out this early."
    "No es que esperara algo diferente. Estaría muy avergonzada si se equivocara tan pronto."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:201
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_da640ee8:

    # k "That's right. Eyes staying nice and closed."
    k "Eso es. Tus ojos se quedan cerrados."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:202
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_325a1f85:

    # k "But if you would happen to forget, your eyes opening on an odd, uneven number that is not even, you may find yourself starting to become hypnotized."
    k "Pero si se te llega a olvidar y tus ojos se abren en un número non, impar, que no es par, tal vez empieces a quedar hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:197
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e17a6860:

    # "Sayori's lip twitches a little at that last word."
    "Los labios de Sayori se tuercen ligeramente con esa última palabra."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:198
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_52ad78ff:

    # "Yeah, she's definitely paying attention to everything."
    "Sí, definitivamente está prestando atención a todo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:205
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9657dcc7:

    # k "Now listen for the next number... {w=0.5} Two, {nw}"
    k "Ahora escucha el siguiente número... {w=0.5}Dos, {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:202
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3e5e1eb4:

    # extend "the second number I've counted, nothing odd about it at all."
    extend "el segundo número que he contado, y no, no noto nada raro."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:209
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ee91c854:

    # k "The sum of one plus one, very easy to remember even if it might become even easier to forget."
    k "La suma de uno más uno, muy fácil de recordar, aunque un par de veces sea más fácil de olvidar."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:204
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2fb38488:

    # "Sayori's lip twitches again as her eyes look to me. I don't know if that's out of anticipation or if she's trying not to laugh."
    "Sayori me mira y sus labios vuelven a torcerse. No sé si es por anticipación o porque intenta no reírse."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:211
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d0559c2c:

    # k "Listening to me, focusing all your attention, Sayori... {w=1.0}Three, {nw}"
    k "Escúchame bien, enfoca toda tu atención, Sayori... {w=1.0}Tres, {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:208
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_09a29103:

    # extend "very odd, Very uneven. Not the fourth number I've counted, or the fifth. Just the third, that's all."
    extend "muy non, muy impar. No el cuarto número del camino, no, ni el quinto. Tan solo es el tercero."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:209
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0fb7bbf5:

    # "Man, I hope this works. It's really hard to talk like this, saying stuff that makes sense but is otherwise a bunch of white noise."
    "Cielos, espero que funcione. Es muy difícil hablar así, diciendo cosas que tienen sentido pero que parecen ruido blanco."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:210
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_72f393fc:

    # "Because that's the thing. Nothing I'm saying is LITERALLY nonsense. Just completely unnecessary and exhausting."
    "Porque esa es la idea. Lo que digo no son LITERALMENTE disparates sin sentido. Tan solo es completamente innecesario y agotador."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:217
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_131b70a8:

    # k "Four now, {nw}"
    k "Y ahora cuatro, {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:214
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_63f5cefd:

    # extend "nothing odd about that number. Unless you forgot, which is easy to do sometimes. It's amazing how we can forget the simplest things."
    extend "pero no, no noto nada raro. A menos que lo hayas olvidado, lo cual a veces es fácil. Es sorprendente cómo podemos olvidar las cosas más simples."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:215
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_679c56fa:

    # "Along with the occasional bit of suggestive language."
    "Junto con una pizca ocasional de lenguaje sugestivo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:216
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2eb8c9e7:

    # "And Sayori needs to listen to every word. Studying them. Finding the trick to what I'm doing."
    "Y Sayori debe escuchar cada palabra. Estudiarlas. Hallarle el truco a lo que estoy haciendo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:223
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0ca3c30d:

    # k "Five. {nw}"
    k "Cinco. {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:220
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_68514656:

    # extend "Another number, very unlike the last number. But also the next number in sequence. Similar yet dissimilar. And on to the next..."
    extend "Otro número, muy distinto al último número. Pero también al próximo número de la secuencia. No es lo mismo, pero es casi igual. Y el siguiente..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:221
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8e81c878:

    # "But if I stopped making any sense at all, she'd soon be able to dismiss it."
    "Pero si dejara de tener sentido, pronto empezaría a ignorarlo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:228
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ad6c5b4a:

    # k "Six now. {nw}"
    k "Ahora seis. {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:225
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b6abef09:

    # extend "An unremarkable, forgettable number. Easy to pass over without thinking."
    extend "Un número poco destacable y olvidable. Fácil de pasar por alto sin pensar."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:226
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e509f31d:

    # "But now that I've established the game, I think it's time to start upping the aggression as I move on quickly."
    "Pero ahora que he establecido el juego, creo que es momento de aumentar la agresión y avanzar rápido."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:233
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_14cb70c3:

    # k "Seven. {nw}"
    k "Siete. {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:230
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_dd021962:

    # extend "That's right, moving past that forgotten number, onto the next. Maybe you like this number more? Who can say. But it's definitely a number."
    extend "Eso es, pasemos de largo ese número olvidable y vamos al siguiente. ¿Quizá este número te gusta más? ¿Quién sabe? Pero claramente es un número."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:231
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d7a055e8:

    # "And then I'll pause right here a few moments. Let her get more comfortable keeping those pretty eyes closed."
    "Y luego hago una pequeña pausa justo aquí. Dejaré que se ponga cómoda manteniendo esos lindos ojitos cerrados."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:238
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b5bccddb:

    # k "But what comes next? {w=0.5}Eight. {nw}"
    k "Pero ¿qué viene después? {w=0.5}Ocho. {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:235
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b03f2a87:

    # extend "{w=0.5}Another unremarkable number. Even and ordinary. Nine."
    extend "{w=0.5}Otro número poco destacable. Par y ordinario. Nueve."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:237
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a5220a6f:

    # "Sayori's eyes flicker before shuttering closed again. A moment's indecision as I moved to the next number even quicker, but it was there. I saw it." with dissolve
    "Los ojos de Sayori se abren y se vuelven a cerrar. Indecisión muy momentánea, pues pasé muy rápido al siguiente número, pero ahí estaba. La vi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:244
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_469826dd:

    # k "So odd, how it becomes easy to forget, or forget to remember, whether your eyes should open or close. Whether to fall deeper into hypnosis, or deeper into hypnosis."
    k "Y bueno, no , no negarás que es fácil olvidar, u olvidar recordar si debes abrir o cerrar. O si debes caer más profundo en hipnosis, o más profundo en hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:246
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a4807f39:

    # "I then reach out and hold my hand above her face, close enough for her to register it but hopefully not imposing enough to completely throw her off." with dissolve
    "Luego pongo mi mano por encima de su rostro, a una distancia a la que pueda verla, pero que espero que no sea tan imponente que la descoloque." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:240
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f9f37841:

    # "I really want to mess with her head now."
    "Quiero hacer de su cabeza un lío."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:248
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_353fbfc9:

    # k "Ten."
    k "Diez."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:244
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7fa5c97e:

    # "Sayori's eyes open and immediately draw themselves upwards, and just then I sweep my hand down her face as I count again." with dissolve
    "Los ojos de Sayori se abren e inmediatamente voltean hacia arriba, y entonces bajo mi mano frente a ella y vuelvo a contar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:253
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e1ed0553:

    # k "Eleven, let's not worry about the evenness of before. Let's just continue onwards and upwards. Relaxing. Deepening. Forgetting." with dissolve
    k "Once, no nos preocupemos por la paridad por ahora. Sigamos yendo arriba y adelante. Más relajante. Más profundo. Más olvido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:255
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3140f66f:

    # "I then raise my hand again and get ready to repeat the trick, albeit with another little curveball she won't be expecting." with dissolve
    "Luego alzo mi mano y me preparo para repetir el truco, aunque con un pequeño giro que seguro no se espera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:256
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_353fbfc9_1:

    # k "Ten."
    k "Diez."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:259
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d1251be9:

    # "Her eyes hesitate to open as she processes what I just said."
    "Sus ojos dudan en abrirse mientras procesa lo que acabo de decir."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:260
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5ecf3dd1:

    # k "Forgettably even, evenly hard to remember, and nine."
    k "Muy olvidable, y a la par difícil de recordar, y nueve."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:253
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_35922651:

    # "Again sweeping my hand down, Sayori's eyes look a little strained as they flutter closed at my prompt." with dissolve
    "Nuevamente bajo mi mano. Los ojos de Sayori lucen algo tensos al cerrarse a mi señal." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:263
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_000cd897:

    # k "A little lower. We could even say deeper now, just taking in the oddness of this state of being you're currently in. Counting. Counting up. Counting down..."
    k "Un poco más bajo. Y podemos ir un par de veces más profundo, si bien no, no notarás la rareza de este estado. Al contar. Contar hacia arriba. Contar hacia abajo..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:264
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2d7efdc2:

    # k "Eight."
    k "Ocho."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:257
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5c3179f5:

    # "Sayori's tiring eyes flicker open and upwards expecting to find my hand above her. Only I left it in my lap this time." with dissolve
    "Los ojos de Sayori se abren y miran arriba esperando encontrar mi mano. Solo que esta vez la dejé en mi regazo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:268
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_275a4bb4:

    # k "Once again, finding how easy it becomes to forget, hard to remember, whether your eyes should open or close." with dissolve
    k "Una vez más, notarás lo fácil que es olvidar, lo difícil que es recordar si tus ojos deben abrirse o cerrarse." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:259
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2e19acc8:

    # "She can't hide her surprise and embarrassedly looks to me again, having nothing else to hold her attention."
    "No puede ocultar la sorpresa y avergonzada vuelve a mirarme, sin nada más en que posar su atención."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:270
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_242e509c:

    # k "And as you remember to forget, or forget to remember, you can find yourself slipping even deeper into hypnosis. Just doubling that state of hypnotic trance."
    k "Y mientras recuerdas olvidar, u olvidas recordar, puedes caer más profundo en hipnosis. Duplicando ese estado de trance hipnótico."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:261
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ccb47e2f:

    # "I can see her frowning. Maybe questioning whether she's actually in trance yet. But it doesn't matter what she thinks."
    "Veo que frunce el ceño. Tal vez cuestionándose si en verdad está ya en trance. Pero no importa lo que piense."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:262
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fde90b51:

    # "She's tired. Her mind's looking for excuses to just shut down completely."
    "Está cansada. Su mente busca excusas para apagarse por completo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:263
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2ef4748d:

    # "Don't worry, Sayori. It's coming."
    "Descuida, Sayori. Ya casi."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:274
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3ca7d6bd:

    # k "Seven. {w=0.5}{nw}"
    k "Siete. {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:267
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4f404b9e:

    # extend "Counting down. Further down. Deeper down. Eyes closed. Or are they open? It's effortless to forget..."
    extend "Contando hacia abajo. Más abajo. Más profundo. Ojos cerrados. ¿O están abiertos? Olvidar es tan sencillo..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:278
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9a9c8376:

    # k "Six."
    k "Seis."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:269
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e1554201_1:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:270
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_896bbf21:

    # "Sayori's eyelids flutter with indecision, but to my quiet delight she keeps them closed. So she really did forget?"
    "Los ojos de Sayori tiemblan con indecisión, pero para mi deleite, los mantiene cerrados. ¿O sea que sí lo olvidó?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:281
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6d11a2c0:

    # k "Five."
    k "Cinco."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:275
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f75df243:

    # "She opened them. Hah, she opened them! Only to snap them shut again when she realized her mistake."
    "Los abrió. ¡Ja, los abrió! Y luego los volvió a cerrar al darse cuenta de su error."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:286
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_256d5507:

    # k "Numbers dropping, thoughts dropping, Even easier to forget and harder to remember. And that sensation will only triple your state of hypnosis."
    k "Los números caen, los pensamientos caen. Es todavía más fácil olvidar y más difícil recordar. Y esa sensación triplicará tu estado de hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:277
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_30428a3e:

    # "She's practically ready to go all the way down now."
    "Está prácticamente lista para caer."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:278
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4a350712:

    # "Just a little more, Sayori."
    "Solo un poco más, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:289
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8c577e3f:

    # k "Three."
    k "Tres."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:282
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_72c3005e:

    # "Her eyes again flicker in anticipation, and again tiredly close when she registers that I skipped a number." with dissolve
    "Sus ojos, de nuevo, se abren con anticipación, y de nuevo, se cierran cuando se da cuenta de que me salté un número." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:283
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7dcad0a3:

    # "I had suggested she forget these even numbers, and perhaps she fought to remember the number four in anticipation after that last mistake."
    "La sugestioné para que olvidara los números pares, y quizá luchó por recordar el número cuatro luego de ese último error."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:284
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fd69bc35:

    # "Too bad."
    "Qué pena."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:295
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_aae57727:

    # k "Descending. Further down than before, always further down. Forgetting more, remembering less..."
    k "Descendiendo. Más profundo que antes, siempre más profundo. Olvidando más, recordando menos..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:296
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0e25b120:

    # k "Two."
    k "Dos."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:289
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fe1b661e:

    # "It's time."
    "Llegó el momento."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:302
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6aa6e102:

    # k "Returning to the second number. Even, so easy to- {nw}"
    k "De regreso al segundo número. Par. Y es muy fácil- {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:305
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5ff5abaa:

    # extend "{w=0.5}one and {nw}"
    extend "{w=0.5}uno y {nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:295
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5eefdcb7:

    # extend "sleep!"
    extend "¡duerme!"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:311
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_958e13bb:

    # k "Descending deeper, Sayori. Forgetting the numbers. {w=0.5}{nw}"
    k "Más profundo, Sayori. Olvidando los números. {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:298
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fb84bb18:

    # extend "Falling deep into hypnotic trance, two times deeper. {w=0.5}{nw}"
    extend "Cayendo en un profundo trance, dos veces más profundo. {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:300
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cdc2d638:

    # extend "Three times deeper. {w=0.5}{nw}"
    extend "Tres veces más profundo. {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:302
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_64ea9d47:

    # extend "Four times deeper..."
    extend "Cuatro veces más profundo..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:319
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9584275d:

    # "I hadn't had cause to click my fingers before, but it seems to work to give Sayori's tired conscious mind the break it needs and drop fully into trance." with dissolve
    "No había tenido razón para chasquear los dedos hasta ahora, pero parece darle a la mente consciente de Sayori la señal que necesita para caer en trance por completo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:322
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_20b696ec:

    # "Next, I gently reach over to take her right wrist and lift it carefully over her lap." with dissolve
    "Posteriormente, tomo con delicadeza el brazo de Sayori y lo elevo cuidadosamente sobre su regazo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:323
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1358d86e:

    # k "That's right, Sayori. Feeling so loose and relaxed. So deeply hypnotized, letting everything else fall away from your sleepy mind."
    k "Eso es, Sayori. Muy flojita y relajada. Muy profundamente hipnotizada. Deja que todo lo demás desaparezca de tu adormecida mente."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:307
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_826daf7a:

    # "Her hand and arm are feeling really floppy right now. That's a really good sign she's where I need her to be."
    "Su mano y brazo se sienten muy blandos. Es una buena señal de que está donde quiero que esté."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:328
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_60b60ca7:

    # "I then carefully drop her hand back in her lap, then pick it up again." with dissolve
    "Luego con cuidado dejo su mano caer de vuelta a su regazo, y la volvo a levantar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:329
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e2c8d7da:

    # k "Feeling your body so limp. Just like a rag doll."
    k "Tu cuerpo se siente muy flojo. Como una muñeca de trapo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:331
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bf17a579:

    # "Letting her hand hover limply for a second more, I then drop it back in her lap where it can stay for the time being." with dissolve
    "Dejo que su mano cuelgue un segundo más, luego vuelvo a soltarla sobre su regazo. Se quedará ahí de momento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:311
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_47d8b669:

    # "If she wasn't convinced about her hypnotic state of mind before, she certainly should be now."
    "Si no estaba convencida de su estado hipnótico, de seguro ahora sí."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:333
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9c8a6995:

    # k "That's right, Sayori. Just like a doll. Isn't that a fun thought?"
    k "Eso es, Sayori. Igual que una muñeca. ¿No es eso divertido?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:313
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3ae35ea1:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Y... yess..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "S... sssíí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:315
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_93eb45c4:

    # "Oh man, her slurred response was immediate. That's kinda hot." with dissolve
    "Oh, cielos, su arrastrada respuesta fue inmediata. Casi se siente sugerente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:338
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_96f37a0d:

    # k "Yes it is. So while you're in this nice, relaxed, deeply suggestible state, let's think about dolls some more."
    k "Sí que lo es. Así que, ahora que estás en este agradable, relajante y profundo estado, pensemos un poco más en muñecas."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:339
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d21caed2:

    # k "Think about how a doll is an inanimate object. It doesn't think. It doesn't move on its own. It simply exists to look pretty for others."
    k "Piensa en cómo una muñeca es un objeto inanimado. No piensa. No se mueve por su cuenta. Tan solo existe para verse bonita para otros."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:340
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_51a667ec:

    # k "Such a carefree existence."
    k "Qué existencia tan despreocupada."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:319
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7a320f20:

    # "I then venture to ask..."
    "Y luego me atrevo a preguntar..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:342
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7e0d2b1d:

    # k "So wouldn't it be nice if, at least for a little while, you could become just like a doll, Sayori?"
    k "¿No sería lindo si, al menos por un rato, pudieras convertirte en una muñeca, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:321
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_76212faa:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Yyesss..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Sssííí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:323
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4cf7513f:

    # "Man, she really does seem to be going for this." with dissolve
    "Caray, en serio parece desear esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:347
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8e4f7d23:

    # k "Good. So here's what's going to happen."
    k "Bien. Entonces esto es lo que va a pasar."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:325
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c59d72d9:

    # "Smiling, I reach down and gently touch the top of her foot as I continue talking gently to her subconscious."
    "Sonriendo, me inclino y toco la punta de su pie, mientras continúo hablando gentilmente con su subconsciente."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:349
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f34e1095:

    # k "Your feet are going to slowly turn from flesh... to plastic."
    k "Tus pies lentamente pasarán de ser carne... a ser plástico."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:350
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e0046c39:

    # k "Becoming hard. Rigid. Immovable."
    k "Se vuelven duros. Rígidos. Inmóviles."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:328
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c12ee72a:

    # "I then slowly start to trail my fingertips up her pants while I continue."
    "Luego empiezo despacio a deslizar las puntas de mis dedos por su pantalón, y continúo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:352
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_80f9d7c0:

    # k "And that hard, rigid plastic spreads from your toes, up your ankles... travelling up your legs..."
    k "Y ese plástico duro y rígido se esparce de tus dedos a tus tobillos... viajando por tus piernas..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:330
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6ac559de:

    # "My hand glides further up her body while I take her on this transformative journey, watching the expression on her face carefully."
    "Mi mano avanza por su cuerpo mientras la guío por este viaje transformador, viendo alegremente la expresión en su rostro."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:354
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8011e4eb:

    # k "Past your hips, your stomach, your chest and your arms... All becoming plastic, Sayori. And that's okay."
    k "Pasando por tus caderas, tu estómago, tu torso y tus brazos... Todo se convierte en plástico, Sayori. Y descuida."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:355
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d89302a3:

    # k "You'll still find you can breathe as you need to."
    k "Notarás que aún puedes respirar con normalidad."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:358
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_885a83f3:

    # k "You still have joints though, Sayori. Your arms and limbs can bend, but a doll can't do that on their own."
    k "Sin embargo aún tienes articulaciones, Sayori. Tus brazos y piernas pueden doblarse, pero una muñeca no puede hacer eso por sí sola."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:359
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_25ed2b9d:

    # k "A doll like you needs someone to move them. You need me. Do you understand, Sayori?"
    k "Una muñeca como tú necesita de alguien que la mueva. Tú me necesitas. ¿Comprendes, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:336
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_76212faa_1:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Yyesss..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Sssííí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:363
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8ebb52dc:

    # k "Very good. Feeling just like a plastic doll with moveable joints." with dissolve
    k "Muy bien. Te sientes como una muñeca de plástico articulada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:365
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_28d27f46:

    # "I'll give her a moment to take in that feeling before moving on." with dissolve
    "Le doy un momento para internalizar esa sensación antes de continuar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:366
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7c0db226:

    # k "And now I want to tell you a phrase that will allow you to immediately become this stiff, jointed plastic doll, any time you're awake and feeling comfortable to do so."
    k "Y ahora voy a decirte una frase que te permitirá convertirte de inmediato en esta rígida muñeca de plástico articulada, cuando estés despierta y te sientas cómoda."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:367
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e2d33259:

    # k "That phrase is \"doll time\". Any time you hear me speak the phrase \"doll time\" and you feel safe and comfortable in doing so..."
    k "Esa frase es \"tiempo de muñeca\". Cada vez que me escuches decir \"tiempo de muñeca\" y te sientas segura y cómoda haciéndolo..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:368
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_df48f86e:

    # k "... you will immediately and automatically find yourself turning back into a plastic doll figure, just like you are now."
    k "... inmediata y automáticamente te transformarás en una figura de plástico como la que eres ahora."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:369
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c814576b:

    # k "Unable to move for yourself. Only able to remain in position until I move you. Understand?"
    k "Incapaz de moverte por tu cuenta. Solo podrás permanecer en posición hasta que yo te mueva. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:344
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5a44e513:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Yes...ss..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Ss... sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:346
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_14606e5f:

    # "She breathes her reply in the sleepy affirmative once again." with dissolve
    "Una vez más, responde de forma afirmativa y soñolienta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:347
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a9251c48:

    # "Are you really any less suggestible than you were with the penlight, Sayori?"
    "¿De verdad eres menos sugestionable de lo que eras con la linterna, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:375
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d5709455:

    # k "Brilliant. Remember that phrase. And there's another phrase I want you to remember."
    k "Espléndido. Recuerda esa frase. Y hay otra frase que quiero que recuerdes."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:376
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_59f94fd5:

    # k "Whenever I speak the phrase \"free time\" to you, you will immediately and effortlessly find yourself returning to your regular human state."
    k "Cuando te diga la frase \"tiempo libre\", regresarás a tu estado humano normal, de inmediato y sin esfuerzo."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:377
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e40125fb:

    # k "You will be free to move as you like as soon as you hear me say \"free time\". Understand?"
    k "Serás libre de moverte tanto como quieras en cuanto escuches esa frase. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:351
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b922f2ad:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Yess..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Ssí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:381
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_172f7e19:

    # k "Very good, Sayori. You really are good at being hypnotized. So in a few moments I'm going to count to five and bring you back to a state of waking." with dissolve
    k "Muy bien, Sayori. Eres muy buena siendo hipnotizada. Así que, en unos momentos, contaré hasta cinco y volverás a despertar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:382
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cb9e01f3:

    # k "And when you wake, you'll be able to move your body as normal, feeling good and refreshed."
    k "Y cuando despiertes, podrás mover tu cuerpo con normalidad, sintiéndote muy fresca."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:383
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_79caf73e:

    # k "Remembering all you can about this state of hypnosis you just experienced."
    k "Recordando todo lo que puedas del estado de hipnosis que acabas de experimentar."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:384
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e00fd609:

    # k "And of course, you will remain very responsive to the phrases I just taught you. Okay, Sayori?"
    k "Y, por supuesto, aún serás responsiva a las frases que te enseñé. ¿De acuerdo, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:357
