# game/Kyou 14.rpy:480
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ddacaf1c:

    # "Makes me want to dress her up in something more flattering than those clothes... but that doesn't seem practical right now."
    "Me hace querer vestirla con algo más favorable que esa ropa... pero eso no parece práctico de momento."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:481
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3e1115f4:

    # "At least I can make her sexier than how she looks right now. Let's see..."
    "Al menos puedo hacer que se vea más sexy que ahora. Veamos..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:482
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5aaebdff:

    # "Taking her outstretched hand, I note how it still yields to my touch as I bend her arm around to have her holding the back of her head."
    "Tomando su mano extendida, noto que sigue dando el brazo a torcer, literalmente, y lo doblo para hacerla sujetar su nuca."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:483
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8ed0ed84:

    # "Next I take the other hand, at her hip, and effortlessly move it to join its counterpart."
    "Luego tomo la otra mano, la cual sigue en su cintura, y sin esfuerzo la muevo para unirla a su contraparte."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:524
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f3d08ed1:

    # "After pulling her elbows a little further apart, I give her back a light push to bring out her chest a bit more."
    "Tras separar un poco sus codos, le doy a su espalda un ligero empujoncito para hacerla sacar un poco el pecho."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:485
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_75351891:

    # "Then... maybe I can push her right knee forward... bend her leg a little. Keep her toes pressed to the floor for balance and..."
    "Después... tal vez pueda mover su rodilla derecha hacia adelante... doblar su pierna un poco. Que sus pies sigan pegados al suelo para equilibrio y..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:486
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3194f688:

    # "Yeah. Stepping back and looking her over, she could almost be a glamour model holding that pose."
    "Sí. Dando un paso atrás y viéndola bien, casi podría ser una modelo de glamour con esa pose."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:487
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_657f7929:

    # "It's so unlike the serious, perpetually tired girl that I've figured Sayori to be."
    "Es tan diferente a la chica seria y perpetuamente cansada que había visto en Sayori."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:488
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_91abbbe3:

    # "Here she looks so carefree, and confident and... and beautiful."
    "Aquí luce tan despreocupada, y confiada y... y hermosa."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:489
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6b32cdcc:

    # "Why did I ever think this woman was ugly?"
    "¿Cómo pude alguna vez pensar que esta mujer era fea?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:494
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_51fe12b2:

    # "Is that weird?"
    "¿Es eso raro?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:496
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b5e25b45:

    # ks "Free time, Sayori."
    ks "Tiempo libre, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:499
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_96607373:

    # "But eventually I'm the one to put an end to it." with dissolve
    "Pero eventualmente, soy yo quien le da cierre." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:500
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e989af13:

    # s casual alert_sleeptalk "Mrrrn..." with dissolve
    s casual alert_sleeptalk "Mmnnn..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:501
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8fe07bad:

    # "Sayori breathes and stretches as she blinks herself slowly back into waking."
    "Sayori respira y se estira, parpadeando mientras despierta lentamente."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:502
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_be09a73c:

    # ks smile "How was it?"
    ks smile "¿Cómo estuvo?"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:505
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_85d2eb75:

    # "She doesn't immediately answer me, instead opting to sit herself down at her table."
    "No me responde de inmediato, y en vez de eso, opta por sentarse en la mesa."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:508
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1839c963:

    # s "Pardon me, but all that standing around has left me feeling a little stiff."
    s "Una disculpa. Pasar tanto tiempo de pie me dejo un poco tiesa."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:512
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9436243f:

    # s alert_sleep "It is very much as if I had been in a meditative state." with dissolve
    s alert_sleep "Fue como si estuviera en un estado de meditación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:513
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_721fc767:

    # s alert_smile "Truly, it was as if my every earthly concern had slipped away and I could simply be. I found it a very pleasant sensation." with dissolve
    s alert_smile "Verdaderamente fue como si todas mis preocupaciones terrenales se hubieran desvanecido y pudiera solo existir. Fue una sensación muy placentera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:522
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e090bc9a:

    # s alert_neutral "I did not experience the kind of helplessness I felt during our previous sessions with the penlight." with dissolve
    s alert_neutral "No experimenté la clase de impotencia que sentí durante nuestras sesiones previas con la linterna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:523
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f2211eff:

    # s alert_sleep "It is difficult to put the sensation into words exactly, just... it does feel different." with dissolve
    s alert_sleep "Es difícil poner con exactitud la sensación en palabras, tan solo... se siente diferente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:526
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_26164f46:

    # "(Author's Note - This is about all I have time for, so the written script for the Doll storyline ends here for now. )"
    "(Nota de la autora – Este es todo el tiempo que me queda, así que el guion escrito para la trama de la Muñeca termina aquí por ahora.)"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:528
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ae2e8d3b:

    # "(What follows now is a rough outline detailing how the story is likely to conclude. You're welcome to read on if you like, or wait for the next update.)"
    "(Lo que viene a continuación es un simple bosquejo, detallando cómo probablemente concluya la historia. Siéntanse libres de leer si lo desean, o esperar a la siguiente actualización.)"

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:713
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fed9562a:

    # "Sayori concludes, following her experience, that the penlight is as dangerous as she thinks and demands Kyou get rid of it, and any notes he took for its construction." with dissolve
    "Sayori concluye, con base en su experiencia, que la linterna es tan peligrosa como piensa, y le exige a Kyou que se deshaga de ella, y de cualquier nota que haya tomada para su construcción." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:714
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_288a6d72:

    # "Kyou might try the usual \"don't we want to know how it works?\" justification for keeping it around and he might have a choice to refuse her, although I'm not keen on that."
    "Puede que Kyou intente lo de siempre \"¿no queremos saber cómo funciona?\", justificaciones para conservarla, y tal vez haya una elección para reusarse, aunque no me gusta mucho la idea."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:718
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0060b663:

    # "So Kyou breaks the penlight and promises to delete his schematics for the penlight when he gets home"
    "Así que Kyou rompe su linterna y promete borrar sus esquemas para la linterna cuando llegue a casa."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:720
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7bb5a65f:

    # "Still, Kyou asks her what now and, well..."
    "Sin embargo, Kyou le pregunta qué pasa ahora y, bueno..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:299
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_53c0fcb6:

    # "Sayori's eyelids flicker once more to look at me."
    "Los párpados de Sayori se levantan una vez más para mirarme."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:300
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b169727a:

    # "Uncertain. Unfocused. Dare I say confused."
    "Dudosos. Desenfocados. Me atrevería a decir confundidos."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:357
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ee5f9c07:

    # "My fingers come to a halt at her shoulder. I thought to go further and touch her head, but... let's not go that far just yet." with dissolve
    "Mis dedos se detienen en su hombro. Pensaba seguir adelante y tocar su cabeza, pero... no vayamos tan lejos todavía." with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-04-09 23:34

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:446
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_88439659:

    # "Smiling, I then step behind her and reach out to gently take her left arm..."
    "Sonriente, camino detrás de ella para tomar su brazo izquierdo con gentileza..."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:459
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_410f85e0:

    # "Next, I turn her wrist and arrange her hand so it's pointed away from her while Sayori can only watch with her eyes."
    "Luego giro su muñeca y acomodo su mano para que quede recta y apuntando a la pared, mientras que Sayori no puede hacer más que mirar."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:461
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f46ff3eb:

    # "My work done, I circle round to stand in front of her and try to look her over with a critical eye..." with dissolve
    "Con mi trabajo ya terminado, la rodeo para posicionarme delante de ella e intento analizarla críticamente..." with dissolve

# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-04-17 23:57

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:454
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_383afe13:

    # "I then, with no small amount of glee, take her right shoulder and pull it carefully, tilting her just a little to her left..."
    "Posteriormente, con gran júbilo, tomo su hombro derecho y tiro suavemente de él, inclinándola un poquitín a su izquierda..."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-05-25 08:08


# game/Kyou 14.rpy:529
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7d0ec3ea:

    # "Satisfied, I reach over and gently hold her chin, lifting her head carefully to face straight ahead."
    "Satisfecho, tomo delicadamente su mentón, levantando con cuidado su cabeza para que mire hacia adelante."

# game/Kyou 14.rpy:541
translate spanish Day14_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_09613502:

    # "And with that, I stroke my thumbs fondly over her warm cheeks as I talk."
    "Y con eso, froto afectuosamente con mis pulgares sus cálidas mejillas mientras hablo."
